[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":188},["ShallowReactive",2],{"team-silvia-serrano-guzman-es":3},{"page":4,"rest":30},{"id":5,"slug":6,"name":7,"role":8,"photo":9,"outline":26,"bio":28,"email":29,"linkedin":20},"OtPTU6GHQhS5GfVPnYlpnw","silvia-serrano-guzman","Silvia Serrano-Guzmán","Co-Directora Ejecutiva",{"id":10,"alt":11,"title":11,"focalPoint":12,"width":14,"height":14,"thumbnail":15,"small":16,"medium":17,"responsiveImage":18,"video":11},"KStwRHp-R_efZJrfuprKIA",null,{"x":13,"y":13},0.5,400,"/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":19,"webpSrcSet":20,"sizes":21,"src":22,"width":14,"height":14,"aspectRatio":23,"alt":11,"title":11,"base64":24,"bgColor":25},"/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 100w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 200w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 300w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 400w","","(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",1,"data:image/jpeg;base64,","#b9825f",{"hex":27},"#115767","\u003Cp>Silvia tambi&eacute;n codirige el Centro para la Salud y los Derechos Humanos del Instituto O'Neill para la Ley Nacional y Global de la Salud de la Universidad de Georgetown, es profesora adjunta en la Facultad de Derecho de Georgetown e imparte clases sobre litigios internacionales en materia de derechos humanos en diferentes universidades de Am&eacute;rica Latina y Europa.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Anteriormente, Silvia fue abogada de la Comisi&oacute;n Interamericana de Derechos Humanos (CIDH) durante 14 a&ntilde;os. Dirigi&oacute; la Secci&oacute;n de Casos, gestionando la cartera de miles de casos relacionados con los 35 Estados miembros de la OEA y siendo responsable del litigio de todos los casos presentados ante la Corte Interamericana de Derechos Humanos.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Silvia obtuvo su t&iacute;tulo de abogada en la Universidad Aut&oacute;noma de Bucaramanga. Tiene un m&aacute;ster en Estudios Jur&iacute;dicos Internacionales y Derecho Internacional de los Derechos Humanos por el Centro de Derecho de la Universidad de Georgetown y un m&aacute;ster en Argumentaci&oacute;n Jur&iacute;dica por la Universidad de Alicante.\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003C/p>","silvia@riossocialjustice.org",[31,55,77,101,121,144,166],{"id":32,"name":33,"slug":34,"role":35,"photo":36,"outline":53},"PRyoLHIvTdS-35tv-G8jUA","Oscar Cabrera","oscar-cabrera","Co-Director Ejecutivo",{"id":37,"alt":11,"title":11,"focalPoint":38,"width":41,"height":42,"thumbnail":43,"small":44,"medium":45,"responsiveImage":46,"video":11},"TkB4dklGSx25yEWY4DmenQ",{"x":39,"y":40},0.45,0.28,480,509,"/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":47,"webpSrcSet":20,"sizes":48,"src":49,"width":41,"height":42,"aspectRatio":50,"alt":11,"title":11,"base64":51,"bgColor":52},"/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 120w,/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 240w,/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 360w,/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 480w","(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px","/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_pic1.jpeg?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",0.9430255402750491,"data:image/jpeg;base64,","#0a9773",{"hex":54},"#D3E173",{"id":56,